---
title: Carb Smart Curd-Stuffed Plant-Based Ground Protein Meatballs  with Cauliflower Mash
description: Juicy plant-based ground protein meatballs get stuffed with squeaky cheese curds in this savoury dinner. Cauliflower mash and roasted carrots are comforting sides for these little stuffed bites of heaven.
